

IMAPStore navin@opencraft.com-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User navin@opencraft.com
PassCmd "pass navin@opencraft.com"
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore navin@opencraft.com-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path /home/navin/.local/share/mail/navin@opencraft.com/
Inbox /home/navin/.local/share/mail/navin@opencraft.com/INBOX

Channel navin@opencraft.com
Expunge Both
Far :navin@opencraft.com-remote:
Near :navin@opencraft.com-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Important" "[Gmail]/Drafts" "[Gmail]Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 1000
ExpireUnread no
CopyArrivalDate yes
# End profile

